data.description: Spacious four-level split home on quiet, desirable street in Boardman Twp. House boasts over 1700 square ft. of space and is situated on a serene, park-like setting on a large lot, with many birds and squirrels visiting in the backyard. On the main floor you will find a generous-sized living room with bright natural light and light hardwood floors in great condition, the dining room and kitchen overlooking the scenic backyard, and access to the two car attached garage. Three bedrooms are upstairs, including the primary bedroom and en suite, and another full bathroom. Go downstairs to the bright and airy den which provides with many possibilities - you could set up as an additional living room, play room, office, or bedroom. From the den, there is another basement level which includes a laundry area and a room which could be used to store tools. Seller has made many upgrades to the home including adding extra blown-in and batting insulation in the attic and under insulation under the vinyl siding, one-piece gutters, vinyl windows, and a radon mitigation system.
